Note before notes¶

  • app: app id for marketing
  • channel: channel id of mobile ad publisher

Notes¶

  • from above we can discover that channelAttrib and appAttrib are usually (model 2,3,4,5) the most important predictors, actually in model 3, 5 these two are the only ones matter
  • linear regression gave us a strange set of variable importance
  • to interpret this, we can say specific channel or app are the most important indicator of whether a click will turn into download, and channel is more important than app
  • thus, deciding where to put your ad (channel) is even more important than your product (app)
  • app1s is probably the third important variable, we can interpret this as a burst of clicks, which may indicate trying to spot robots (and ignore them?) is useful for us to locate potential downloads
